---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Community Mental Health | HealthPsyche and CareBridge Initiatives">

<!-- HERO -->

<section
  class="relative h-[75vh] bg-cover bg-center"
  style="background-image:url('/images/gallery/community-1/1.jpg');"
>

  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/65"></div>

  <div
    class="relative z-10 h-full flex items-center justify-center px-8"
  >

    <div class="max-w-5xl text-center">

      <p
        class="uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-green-300 font-semibold mb-6"
      >

        COMMUNITY MENTAL HEALTH

      </p>

      <h1
        class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight"
      >

        Building

        <span class="text-green-300">

          Healthier Communities

        </span>

      </h1>

      <p
        class="mt-10 text-xl text-white leading-10"
      >

        Promoting mental wellbeing through awareness,
        education, advocacy and community engagement.

      </p>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- INTRODUCTION -->

<section class="py-24 bg-white">

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-8 text-center">

    <h2
      class="text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
    >

      Everyone Deserves Good Mental Health

    </h2>

    <p
      class="mt-10 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700"
    >

      HealthPsyche and CareBridge Initiatives (HPCBI)
      believes that strong communities begin with healthy
      minds. Through community-based education,
      sensitisation campaigns and practical support, we
      help individuals and families better understand
      mental health and wellbeing.

    </p>

    <p
      class="mt-8 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700"
    >

      We work alongside schools, community leaders,
      organisations and volunteers to reduce stigma,
      encourage early support-seeking and promote healthier
      lifestyles for people of all ages.

    </p>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- WHAT WE DO -->
<section class="py-24 bg-slate-50">

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">

    <div class="text-center">

      <p
        class="uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-green-600 font-semibold"
      >

        OUR WORK

      </p>

      <h2
        class="mt-6 text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
      >

        What We Do

      </h2>

      <p
        class="mt-8 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
      >

        Our community mental health initiatives are designed
        to educate, empower and inspire healthier
        communities through evidence-based programmes and
        meaningful partnerships.

      </p>

    </div>

    <div
      class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mt-20"
    >

      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl p-10 text-center">

        <div class="text-5xl">


        </div>

        <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-bold">

          Mental Health Awareness

        </h3>

        <p class="mt-5 text-gray-600 leading-8">

          Delivering community education that increases
          understanding of mental health, reduces stigma and
          encourages early support.

        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl p-10 text-center">

        <div class="text-5xl">


        </div>

        <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-bold">

          Public Health Promotion

        </h3>

        <p class="mt-5 text-gray-600 leading-8">

          Promoting healthy lifestyles through awareness on
          disease prevention, immunisation and overall
          wellbeing.

        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl p-10 text-center">

        <div class="text-5xl">


        </div>

        <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-bold">

          Community Outreach

        </h3>

        <p class="mt-5 text-gray-600 leading-8">

          Working directly with schools, neighbourhoods,
          faith-based organisations and community groups to
          deliver practical health education.

        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl p-10 text-center">

        <div class="text-5xl">


        </div>

        <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-bold">

          Advocacy & Partnerships

        </h3>

        <p class="mt-5 text-gray-600 leading-8">

          Collaborating with government agencies, NGOs,
          development partners and community leaders to
          expand access to quality mental health services.

        </p>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- OUR COMMUNITY APPROACH -->
<section class="py-24 bg-white">

  <div
    class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center"
  >

    <div>

      <img
        src="/images/gallery/community-1/2.jpg"
        alt="Community-1"
        class="rounded-3xl shadow-2xl w-full object-cover"
      />

    </div>

    <div>

      <p
        class="uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-green-600 font-semibold"
      >

        OUR APPROACH

      </p>

      <h2
        class="mt-6 text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
      >

        Community-Led, People-Centred Solutions

      </h2>

      <p
        class="mt-8 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700"
      >

        We believe lasting change happens when communities
        are actively involved in identifying their needs and
        working together to develop practical solutions.
        Every programme is designed to encourage
        participation, build trust and strengthen local
        capacity.

      </p>

      <p
        class="mt-6 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700"
      >

        Through partnerships with schools, community
        associations, faith-based organisations, youth
        groups and public institutions, HPCBI delivers
        sustainable initiatives that improve health,
        wellbeing and social inclusion.

      </p>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- COMMUNITY IMPACT -->

<section class="py-24 bg-slate-50">

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">

    <div class="text-center">

