        </p>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- CALL TO ACTION -->

<section
  class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-700 to-blue-700"
>

  <div
    class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 text-center"
  >

    <h2
      class="text-7xl font-bold text-white"
    >

      Let's Build Healthier Communities Together

    </h2>

    <p
      class="mt-8 text-xl text-white leading-9"
    >

      Whether you represent a community association,
      government agency, NGO, school or corporate
      organisation, we welcome opportunities to work
      together to improve health and wellbeing.

    </p>

    <div
      class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6"
    >

      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="bg-white text-green-700 font-bold px-10 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-100 transition"
      >

        Contact Us

      </a>

      <a
        href="/support-our-mission"
        class="bg-green-900 text-white font-bold px-10 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-green-800 transition"
